name: User can add a new card on any list on the current board
description: As a user, I should be able to manage my works by creating a new board/list/card and modifying them under Deck Module.
descriptionHtml: As a user, I should be able to manage my works by creating a new board/list/card and modifying them under Deck Module.

testStage.description: As a user, I should be able to manage my works by creating a new board/list/card and modifying them under Deck Module.

steps.name: Given  the user logs in with username "Employee80" and password "Employee123"
And  the user navigates to the Deck page
And  the user clicks on app navigation toggle
When  the user clicks on any board with name "Operational Excellence"
And  the user adds a new card "Lean Six Sigma" to list "Process Improvements"
Then  the new card "Lean Six Sigma" should be visible in list "Process Improvements"

labels.name: story
labels.value: User can add a new card on any list on the current board
